org.microtitan.diffusive.diffuser.restful.response

Interface DiffuserResponse

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDiffuserResponse, CreateDiffuserResponse, DeleteDiffuserResponse, ExecuteDiffuserResponse, ListDiffuserResponse

    public interface DiffuserResponse
    Essentially wraps the Feed that is returned as a response from the RestfulDiffuserManagerResource into a Java class that can be access in a traditional object-oriented manner.
    Author:
    Robert Philipp
